patterns.title: Promotion gates disconnected from practical run capacity
patterns.evidence: live_query gate N=300, median observed N=10 (30x gap). Power at practical cap: 11-23%. All 3 classes PROVISIONAL after 163 artifacts. Effect threshold dispersion 6.28x for simulation class.

patterns.title: Reporting quality 100% but pickup rate 0% for schema-contract lanes
patterns.evidence: 5 lanes scored 1.0 on 7-key contract. Schema-contract: 0/15 picked up (0%). Free-form: 7/16 picked up (43.75%). Replicates across 2 independent runs.

patterns.title: I2>75% is structural property, not sampling noise — pooling destroys information
patterns.evidence: IS family I2=77-84% across 6 runs (k=21 to k=33). Finance I2=0% in every run. Pooled effect changed conclusion from composition, not mechanism. Effect range within IS: +0.049 to -0.768.

patterns.title: BH vs Bonferroni identical for p<1e-4, diverge only at margin
patterns.evidence: All runs k<25: BH=Bonferroni. k=33: BH=4, Bonferroni=2. Divergence at p~0.001. Core discoveries (p=3.4e-5, p=2.4e-5) correction-invariant.

patterns.title: Conclusion flipped without new mechanism — 7 more IS variants drove it
patterns.evidence: k=26 inconclusive → k=33 negative-transfer-signal. Only IS studies added. Finance unchanged. No new domain or metric.

patterns.title: Experiment class defined by method, not mechanism, produces unlockable gates
patterns.evidence: lane_log_extraction contains f-evo2 (N=48, effect=0.417), f-is5 (N=28, effect=0.075), f-ctl3 (N=8, effect=1.779). Sign_stability=0.5 (random). 20x effect range within class.

finance_null_result.description: Finance factual QA: I2=0%, pooled effect ±0.005, 0 discoveries in 15 studies across multiple sample sizes. Clean replicable null.
finance_null_result.implication: Swarm iteration on factual QA tasks does not improve accuracy in this domain.
